songs.title: Con-Science
songs.lyrics:

I can’t pretend
Choose how it ends
Years slipped away
Questions here to stay

[Chorus]
In fear
In soul
In fear
In soul

[Verse 2]
I can’t pretend
Consumed by an ens
Try bend the rules
Ripped out recluse

[Chorus]
In fear
In soul
In fear
In soul

[Verse 3]
I can’t pretend
Choose how it ends
Years slipped away
Questions here to stay

[Chorus]
In soul
In fear
In soul
In fear

In fear
In soul
In fear
In soul
